<p>Session voting and optimization is a fine idea. As mentioned in a previous comment, using SMS may be an inexpensive and easy way to go.</p>

<p>I would like to see such meetings have some sort of loose goal (perhaps create one or more once the group is assembled). Again, pitches and quiet expressions of interest may help.</p>

<p>Offering suggestions for subsequent year invitees may be better toward the middle of the meeting instead of the beginning.</p>

